updates_from_previous_fiscal_note: The current analysis, based on testimony and the committee report for HB70 HD1, corroborates the conclusions of the previous fiscal note. There are no substantive changes to the fiscal assessment, as the bill continues to have no direct financial impact on the State of Hawaii. The previous note's update referencing a later version of the bill (HB70 HD1 SD1) and a different effective date is not relevant to the current documents provided for HB70 HD1.
